00:54:02,679 --> 00:54:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi ćemo.

1111
00:54:03,000 --> 00:54:06,739
[SPEAKER_00] Župnik moj gdje sam bio u Rimu.

1112
00:54:06,739 --> 00:54:08,619
[SPEAKER_00] Znači kao žako na praktiku.

1113
00:54:08,619 --> 00:54:09,400
[SPEAKER_00] Moj imao jednu majicu.

1114
00:54:09,400 --> 00:54:10,179
[SPEAKER_00] Je dobio na poklon.

1115
00:54:10,179 --> 00:54:11,019
[SPEAKER_00] I onda joj iza kreveta.

1116
00:54:11,019 --> 00:54:13,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ovako je na čovlima joj zakucao

1117
00:54:13,159 --> 00:54:13,820
[SPEAKER_00] iznad kreveta.

1118
00:54:13,820 --> 00:54:15,420
[SPEAKER_00] I na toj majici je pisalo

1119
00:54:15,420 --> 00:54:16,679
[SPEAKER_00] Kalmati.

1120
00:54:16,679 --> 00:54:18,360
[SPEAKER_00] I ođa salvato il mondo.

1121
00:54:18,360 --> 00:54:20,099
[SPEAKER_00] Smiri se.

1122
00:54:20,099 --> 00:54:21,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam već spasio svijet.

1123
00:54:21,679 --> 00:54:25,159
[SPEAKER_00] Odlična poruka.

1124
00:54:28,760 --> 00:54:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] Što učiniti u tim situacijama?

1125
00:54:30,539 --> 00:54:33,699
[SPEAKER_00] Sigurno da trebamo reći

1126
00:54:33,699 --> 00:54:34,760
[SPEAKER_00] ukoliko nas smeta.

1127
00:54:34,760 --> 00:54:36,139
[SPEAKER_00] Znači ako me smeta ga neko psuje

1128
00:54:36,139 --> 00:54:36,960
[SPEAKER_00] trebamo reći gledajte

1129
00:54:36,960 --> 00:54:38,719
[SPEAKER_00] mene to stvarno smeta.

1130
00:54:38,719 --> 00:54:41,320
[SPEAKER_00] Prva stvar koju mogu uvijek učiniti je

1131
00:54:41,320 --> 00:54:42,300
[SPEAKER_00] dignuti se i otići.

1132
00:54:42,300 --> 00:54:43,980
[SPEAKER_00] To sam uvijek slobodan učiniti.

1133
00:54:43,980 --> 00:54:47,139
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ako sam s tim osobama tamo

1134
00:54:47,139 --> 00:54:48,460
[SPEAKER_00] i ako one konkretno ustraju

1135
00:54:48,460 --> 00:54:49,699
[SPEAKER_00] stalno u tom psovanju

1136
00:54:49,699 --> 00:54:51,440
[SPEAKER_00] onda ja neću ništa dobra od njih dobiti.

1137
00:54:51,440 --> 00:54:52,619
[SPEAKER_00] Onda je bolje da se maknem.

1138
00:54:52,619 --> 00:54:54,460
[SPEAKER_00] To je prva stvar.

1139
00:54:54,460 --> 00:54:55,639
[SPEAKER_00] Druga stvar.

1140
00:54:55,639 --> 00:54:57,340
[SPEAKER_00] Znači mogu uvijek upozoriti.

1141
00:54:57,340 --> 00:54:58,079
[SPEAKER_00] trebamo upozoriti.

1142
00:54:58,079 --> 00:55:00,940
[SPEAKER_00] Reći meni to smeta.

1143
00:55:00,940 --> 00:55:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ja toga boga ili te psovke

1144
00:55:03,960 --> 00:55:05,539
[SPEAKER_00] koje ja tog boga volim.

1145
00:55:05,539 --> 00:55:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] I vi psujete nešto što ja volim.

1146
00:55:09,000 --> 00:55:11,300
[SPEAKER_00] Molim vas nemojte to činiti.

1147
00:55:11,300 --> 00:55:13,820
[SPEAKER_00] Reći ću vam opet jednu situaciju

1148
00:55:13,820 --> 00:55:14,639
[SPEAKER_00] koja mi se dogodila.

1149
00:55:14,639 --> 00:55:18,980
[SPEAKER_00] Kolega, svećenik, brat svećenik i ja

1150
00:55:18,980 --> 00:55:19,960
[SPEAKER_00] idemo na picu

1151
00:55:19,960 --> 00:55:21,659
[SPEAKER_00] i dolazimo u pizzeriju

1152
00:55:21,659 --> 00:55:23,679
[SPEAKER_00] i sjednemo i sad sjedimo

1153
00:55:23,679 --> 00:55:24,679
[SPEAKER_00] iza nas.

1154
00:55:24,679 --> 00:55:25,760
[SPEAKER_00] Znači ovdje sjedim ja,

1155
00:55:25,760 --> 00:55:26,659
[SPEAKER_00] on ovdje

1156
00:55:26,659 --> 00:55:27,579
[SPEAKER_00] iza mene

1157
00:55:27,579 --> 00:55:28,780
[SPEAKER_00] jedna grupica,

1158
00:55:28,780 --> 00:55:29,860
[SPEAKER_00] jedna od njih pet, šest

1159
00:55:29,860 --> 00:55:31,099
[SPEAKER_00] ovak frajeri

1160
00:55:31,099 --> 00:55:33,239
[SPEAKER_00] i deru li ga deru.

1161
00:55:33,239 --> 00:55:35,199
[SPEAKER_00] Deru li ga deru,

1162
00:55:35,199 --> 00:55:35,619
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

1163
00:55:35,619 --> 00:55:36,679
[SPEAKER_00] od,

1164
00:55:36,679 --> 00:55:38,820
[SPEAKER_00] od, od, od, od.

1165
00:55:44,400 --> 00:55:45,840
[SPEAKER_00] čekamo mi picu.

1166
00:55:45,840 --> 00:55:47,260
[SPEAKER_00] Čekamo mi picu,

1167
00:55:47,260 --> 00:55:48,380
[SPEAKER_00] odužila se ta pica.

1168
00:55:48,380 --> 00:55:49,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ja lud, ne mogu više,

1169
00:55:49,659 --> 00:55:50,619
[SPEAKER_00] znaš, teško mi je.

1170
00:55:50,619 --> 00:55:53,659
[SPEAKER_00] I ja u sebi molim.

1171
00:55:53,659 --> 00:55:55,719
[SPEAKER_00] Molim, blagosljivljam ih,

1172
00:55:55,719 --> 00:55:57,219
[SPEAKER_00] molim za njih onako,

1173
00:55:57,219 --> 00:55:59,980
[SPEAKER_00] trudim se s njim razgovarati,

1174
00:55:59,980 --> 00:56:02,179
[SPEAKER_00] biti prisutan i njih blagosljivljati isto nije baš lako,

1175
00:56:02,179 --> 00:56:03,320
[SPEAKER_00] ali evo, trudim se i tako.

1176
00:56:03,320 --> 00:56:05,800
[SPEAKER_00] I završimo, mi pojedemo u picu

1177
00:56:05,800 --> 00:56:06,340
[SPEAKER_00] i dignemo se,

1178
00:56:06,340 --> 00:56:07,500
[SPEAKER_00] idemo sada ovaj platiti.

1179
00:56:07,780 --> 00:56:08,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne mogu,

1180
00:56:08,500 --> 00:56:09,300
[SPEAKER_00] ne mogu jednostavno.

1181
00:56:09,300 --> 00:56:10,920
[SPEAKER_00] Kažem, nisam ni bio u njihovom društvu,

1182
00:56:10,920 --> 00:56:11,739
[SPEAKER_00] nego jednostavno je bilo tu,

1183
00:56:11,739 --> 00:56:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] stol pored.

1184
00:56:12,599 --> 00:56:13,840
[SPEAKER_00] I dođem.

1185
00:56:13,840 --> 00:56:16,519
[SPEAKER_00] I jednom koji je baš onako ustraje u Bogu,

1186
00:56:16,519 --> 00:56:17,900
[SPEAKER_00] baš Bogopsovki, baš jako.

1187
00:56:17,900 --> 00:56:18,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ja dođem do njega i kažem,

1188
00:56:18,940 --> 00:56:19,500
[SPEAKER_00] prijatelju,

1189
00:56:19,500 --> 00:56:21,159
[SPEAKER_00] ali nisam bio obučen kao svećanik,

1190
00:56:21,159 --> 00:56:22,360
[SPEAKER_00] prijatelju,

1191
00:56:22,360 --> 00:56:25,280
[SPEAKER_00] a šta ti je učinio loše?

1192
00:56:25,280 --> 00:56:28,760
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ono gledam,

1193
00:56:28,760 --> 00:56:29,300
[SPEAKER_00] možete misliti,

1194
00:56:29,300 --> 00:56:30,320
[SPEAKER_00] ono ovaj se pojavi otkud

1195
00:56:30,320 --> 00:56:31,699
[SPEAKER_00] i ono pita još šta ti je učinio loše.

1196
00:56:31,699 --> 00:56:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ko?

1197
00:56:33,619 --> 00:56:35,019
[SPEAKER_00] A kažem, onaj kojeg ja volim,

1198
00:56:35,019 --> 00:56:36,579
[SPEAKER_00] Bog.

1199
00:56:36,579 --> 00:56:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] A zašto ga toliko psuješ?

1200
00:56:40,000 --> 00:56:42,519
[SPEAKER_00] U tom trenutku,

1201
00:56:42,519 --> 00:56:44,260
[SPEAKER_00] ovi ostali oko njega,

1202
00:56:44,260 --> 00:56:45,420
[SPEAKER_00] su rekli,

1203
00:56:45,420 --> 00:56:47,119
[SPEAKER_00] dobro si mu rekao.

1204
00:56:47,119 --> 00:56:50,059
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su me podržali.

1205
00:56:50,059 --> 00:56:55,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ne treba se bojati.

1206
00:56:55,320 --> 00:56:56,860
[SPEAKER_00] Reći.

1207
00:56:56,860 --> 00:57:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ko će li uvijek uspjeti?

1208
00:57:00,000 --> 00:57:00,360
[SPEAKER_00] Neće.

1209
00:57:00,360 --> 00:57:01,619
[SPEAKER_00] Nekad ćemo biti ismijani,

1210
00:57:01,619 --> 00:57:02,400
[SPEAKER_00] bit ćemo svašto,

1211
00:57:02,500 --> 00:57:04,139
[SPEAKER_00] ali samo to prikaži gospodinu,

1212
00:57:04,139 --> 00:57:06,480
[SPEAKER_00] reci hvala ti Isuse što sam ti mogla biti slična.

1213
00:57:06,480 --> 00:57:07,900
[SPEAKER_00] Pa njega su ismijavali.

1214
00:57:07,900 --> 00:57:09,820
[SPEAKER_00] Smajte koje je milosti

1215
00:57:09,820 --> 00:57:11,199
[SPEAKER_00] da budemo njemu slični.

1216
00:57:11,199 --> 00:57:14,079
[SPEAKER_00] A nekada će i uspjeti.

1217
00:57:14,079 --> 00:57:16,420
[SPEAKER_00] Je li on sad promijenio svoj život

1218
00:57:16,420 --> 00:57:17,300
[SPEAKER_00] prestao psovat Boga?

1219
00:57:17,300 --> 00:57:20,380
[SPEAKER_00] Daj Bože.

1220
00:57:20,380 --> 00:57:21,719
[SPEAKER_00] Daj Bože.

1221
00:57:21,719 --> 00:57:23,500
[SPEAKER_00] Teško, ali daj Bože.

1222
00:57:23,500 --> 00:57:26,179
[SPEAKER_00] Ali da će se sjetiti sljedeći put

1223
00:57:26,179 --> 00:57:27,280
[SPEAKER_00] kad opsuje Boga mene,

1224
00:57:27,280 --> 00:57:28,780
[SPEAKER_00] sigurno hoće.

1225
00:57:31,380 --> 00:57:32,800
[SPEAKER_00] i da sam ja rekao da ga volim.

1226
00:57:32,800 --> 00:57:37,699
[SPEAKER_00] Božja ljubav mijenja.

1227
00:57:37,699 --> 00:57:39,820
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujte mi, Božja ljubav mijenja.

1228
00:57:39,820 --> 00:57:40,739
[SPEAKER_00] Bože ljubav je

1229
00:57:40,739 --> 00:57:43,500
[SPEAKER_00] naše spasenje.

1230
00:57:43,500 --> 00:57:44,280
[UNKNOWN] Da.

1231
00:57:44,280 --> 00:57:46,179
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam se ti uspio odgovoriti.

1232
00:57:47,780 --> 00:57:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Malo još koje je pitanje.

1233
00:57:49,000 --> 00:58:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] Životna ispovjed je dosta kompliciran pojam.

1234
00:58:02,539 --> 00:58:02,940
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

1235
00:58:02,940 --> 00:58:07,539
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što, znači, svaki put kad mi dođemo iskreno na svetu ispovjed,

1236
00:58:07,539 --> 00:58:09,460
[SPEAKER_00] znači ukoliko želimo sve donijeti gospodinu,

1237
00:58:09,460 --> 00:58:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] sve nam je oprošteno, svi grijesi.

1238
00:58:11,719 --> 00:58:13,840
[SPEAKER_00] Čak i oni koji se u tom trenutku ne možemo sjetiti.

1239
00:58:13,840 --> 00:58:16,739
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, to je jedan od ovih stvari skrupuloznosti.

1240
00:58:16,739 --> 00:58:18,440
[SPEAKER_00] Često puta skrupuloznost može biti ono,

1241
00:58:18,440 --> 00:58:20,760
[SPEAKER_00] joj, ako nisam sve rekao, jel mi Bog sve oprostio?

1242
00:58:20,840 --> 00:58:26,179
[SPEAKER_00] Je, ako si iskreno srca došao u tu svetu ispovjed sa željom

1243
00:58:26,179 --> 00:58:28,219
[SPEAKER_00] da sve predaš gospodinu, sve ti je oprošteno.

1244
00:58:28,219 --> 00:58:32,280
[SPEAKER_00] E ako je sve oprošteno, čemu onda životna ispovjed?

1245
00:58:32,280 --> 00:58:38,340
[SPEAKER_00] Zato taj termin životna ispovjed, po meni, nije dobar.

1246
00:58:38,340 --> 00:58:43,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ali okej, ušao je nekako u našu naviku, koristenje,

1247
00:58:43,960 --> 00:58:46,219
[SPEAKER_00] koristimo ga, pa okej, nek stoji sad. Zašto?

1248
00:58:46,219 --> 00:58:49,179
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što nije loše s vremena na vrijeme,

1249
00:58:50,619 --> 00:58:53,860
[SPEAKER_00] proći svoj život s gospodinom.

1250
00:58:53,860 --> 00:58:58,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ali opet se vraćamo na konfesio laudis.

1251
00:58:58,340 --> 00:59:01,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ne samo svoje grijehe, nego i lijepe trenutke

1252
00:59:01,519 --> 00:59:03,079
[SPEAKER_00] što mi je gospodin darovao u životu.

1253
00:59:03,079 --> 00:59:04,780
[SPEAKER_00] Prolazim s njim.

1254
00:59:04,780 --> 00:59:08,380
[SPEAKER_00] A isto tako i prolazim te grijehe, te moje padove

1255
00:59:08,380 --> 00:59:10,639
[SPEAKER_00] zajedno s njim i predajem ih njemu.

1256
00:59:10,639 --> 00:59:12,460
[SPEAKER_00] Znači u tom sakramentu.

1257
00:59:12,460 --> 00:59:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ali uvijek treba naglasiti, znači da je to već oprošteno

1258
00:59:16,579 --> 00:59:18,579
[SPEAKER_00] u ispovjedi, kada smo došli iskreno.

1259
00:59:19,400 --> 00:59:21,500
[SPEAKER_00] Znači nije da su ti grijesi prisutni.

1260
00:59:21,500 --> 00:59:21,860
[SPEAKER_00] Nisu.

1261
00:59:21,860 --> 00:59:25,179
[SPEAKER_00] Ali što je ono što u stvari muči čovjeka koji traži

1262
00:59:25,179 --> 00:59:27,300
[SPEAKER_00] životnu ispovjedu je to što on ne može oprostiti sam sebi.

1263
00:59:27,300 --> 00:59:29,280
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je već njemu oprostio.

1264
00:59:29,280 --> 00:59:30,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ali on ne može sam sebi.

1265
00:59:30,739 --> 00:59:31,780
[SPEAKER_00] Zato treba biti strpljiv.

1266
00:59:31,780 --> 00:59:33,059
[SPEAKER_00] I dopustiti.

1267
00:59:33,059 --> 00:59:33,760
[SPEAKER_00] Neka prođe.

1268
00:59:33,760 --> 00:59:36,760
[SPEAKER_00] Kroz taj razgovor cijela ta životna ispovjeda.

1269
00:59:37,760 --> 00:59:38,780
[SPEAKER_00] U tom smislu.

1270
00:59:38,780 --> 00:59:46,940
[SPEAKER_00] I da se po njoj posvijesti pravo ta Božja ljubav koja je prisutna kroz cijeli život.

1271
00:59:46,940 --> 00:59:48,739
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko je Bog bio prisutan.

1272
00:59:48,739 --> 00:59:50,280
[SPEAKER_00] Kroz cijeli život.

1273
00:59:50,280 --> 00:59:55,360
[SPEAKER_00] I zato smatram da, ako se ono možda pitanje jesi li ti za to, često znaju biti,

1274
00:59:55,360 --> 00:59:57,380
[SPEAKER_00] jesu ti li vi veličasni za životnu ispovjedu.

1275
00:59:58,440 --> 01:00:02,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam za to da se Bogu, da se tom čovjeku pokaže da ga Bog ljubi.

1276
01:00:02,019 --> 01:00:04,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ćemo to kroz ovo, može.

1277
01:00:04,920 --> 01:00:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] I svjedok sam, često su ljudi dolazili na životnu ispovjedu od mene,

1278
01:00:10,079 --> 01:00:12,099
[SPEAKER_00] svjedok sam da se to stvarno događa u tome.

1279
01:00:12,099 --> 01:00:16,900
[SPEAKER_00] Da osjete da su ljubljeni i da to bude prekretnica njihovog života.

1280
01:00:16,900 --> 01:00:18,480
[SPEAKER_00] To bude jedan novi početak zaista.

1281
01:00:18,480 --> 01:00:22,480
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, evo, ne znam, ne sam uspio ovaj.

1282
01:00:22,480 --> 01:00:27,940
[SPEAKER_00] Malo još koje pitanje?

1283
01:00:28,440 --> 01:00:29,300
[SPEAKER_00] Izvoli.

1284
01:00:29,300 --> 01:00:38,699
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ovdje sam toga doživio ovako.

1285
01:00:38,699 --> 01:00:44,679
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, što mislim o mobitelima u ispovjdaonici?

1286
01:00:44,679 --> 01:00:51,219
[SPEAKER_00] Mobitel u ispovjdaonici, ovaj, sad već 9.15, dobro, okej, budemo,

1287
01:00:51,219 --> 01:00:52,699
[SPEAKER_00] je li vam dosadno?

1288
01:00:52,699 --> 01:00:56,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, dobro, okej, dobro.

1289
01:00:56,739 --> 01:00:59,199
[SPEAKER_00] Mobitel u ispovjdaonici, što mislim o tome?

1290
01:00:59,199 --> 01:01:04,019
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam za to. Zašto?

1291
01:01:04,019 --> 01:01:08,559
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što po meni je to bliže ovom drugom sinu,

1292
01:01:08,559 --> 01:01:11,559
[SPEAKER_00] i znači konkretno sad to ja moram držati,

1293
01:01:11,559 --> 01:01:13,760
[SPEAKER_00] moram to točno sve izreći, kako sam tu zapisao,

1294
01:01:13,760 --> 01:01:14,460
[SPEAKER_00] sve to točno,

1295
01:01:15,800 --> 01:01:20,739
[SPEAKER_00] nego ovom prvom da tražim Božju ljubav i da tražim oca koji će me zagrliti i poljubiti

1296
01:01:20,739 --> 01:01:24,500
[SPEAKER_00] i kojem vjerujem da mi je sve oprošteno ako mu dođe miskena srca.

1297
01:01:27,619 --> 01:01:30,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je nekome teško zapamtiti svoje grijehe,

1298
01:01:30,340 --> 01:01:33,940
[SPEAKER_00] možda sam čak više za papir da se napiše na papir,

1299
01:01:33,940 --> 01:01:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] nisam baš za mobitel, mobitel su čudna stvar.

1300
01:01:37,039 --> 01:01:39,300
[SPEAKER_00] Imam jednog svećenika prijatelja koji je,

1301
01:01:39,300 --> 01:01:41,079
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam ja došao sa ispovjedinjemu,

1302
01:01:41,079 --> 01:01:42,539
[SPEAKER_00] onda mi je rekao daj mi svoj mobitel.

1303
01:01:42,539 --> 01:01:45,019
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je oba mobitela, i svoj i moj,

1304
01:01:45,019 --> 01:01:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] stavio drugu sobu.

1305
01:01:47,340 --> 01:01:47,699
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

1306
01:01:47,699 --> 01:01:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] A ja vjerujem da to mi potvrđali smo ljudi

1307
01:01:51,079 --> 01:01:52,860
[SPEAKER_00] da se može prisuškivat preko mobitela,

1308
01:01:52,860 --> 01:01:56,099
[SPEAKER_00] čak i kad je samo ovakav, kakav je sad.

1309
01:01:56,099 --> 01:01:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] Znači to je što se tiče mobitela,

1310
01:01:59,099 --> 01:02:00,559
[SPEAKER_00] znači konkretno za mobitela nisam.

1311
01:02:00,559 --> 01:02:03,079
[SPEAKER_00] Za papir možda jesam, ali ne uvijek.

1312
01:02:03,079 --> 01:02:04,280
[SPEAKER_00] Za početak da,

1313
01:02:04,280 --> 01:02:07,019
[SPEAKER_00] ali rast u ovome, u ovoj očevoj ljubavi,

1314
01:02:07,019 --> 01:02:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] u ovome da je to sakramenat koji primam.

1315
01:02:09,440 --> 01:02:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ova prispodoba, da se to događa.

1316
01:02:13,000 --> 01:02:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda ću s vremenom stvarno shvati da je...

1317
01:02:16,880 --> 01:02:19,500
[SPEAKER_00] ali i druga stvar je ova disciplina.

1318
01:02:19,500 --> 01:02:21,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ako si odredim svaka dva tjedna,

1319
01:02:21,360 --> 01:02:22,639
[SPEAKER_00] svaki mjese dana ispovjedanje

1320
01:02:22,639 --> 01:02:24,579
[SPEAKER_00] i onda radim ispit, savjest ili dovito,

1321
01:02:24,579 --> 01:02:25,599
[SPEAKER_00] recimo, svaki dan,

1322
01:02:25,599 --> 01:02:27,280
[SPEAKER_00] zapisujem sve te stvari

1323
01:02:27,280 --> 01:02:29,139
[SPEAKER_00] i onda vidim otprilike te grijehe

1324
01:02:29,139 --> 01:02:30,900
[SPEAKER_00] i već doma ih mogu, znači, potregati

1325
01:02:30,900 --> 01:02:31,860
[SPEAKER_00] i donijeti u ispovedalnicu.

1326
01:02:31,860 --> 01:02:32,719
[SPEAKER_00] Ili kažem, ako je,

1327
01:02:32,719 --> 01:02:34,780
[SPEAKER_00] barem onda neka bude na papiru.

1328
01:02:34,780 --> 01:02:35,440
[SPEAKER_00] U tom smislu.

1329
01:02:35,440 --> 01:02:36,300
[SPEAKER_00] Evo.

1330
01:02:36,300 --> 01:02:39,820
[SPEAKER_00] Samo špio, jesam.

1331
01:02:39,820 --> 01:02:40,719
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam, jesam.

1332
01:02:40,719 --> 01:02:41,059
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro.

1333
01:02:41,059 --> 01:02:41,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1334
01:02:41,539 --> 01:02:42,300
[SPEAKER_00] Izvoli.

1335
01:02:46,420 --> 01:02:51,900
[SPEAKER_00] Pa jučer, jučer,

1336
01:02:51,900 --> 01:02:53,079
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam koji je bio na misi jučer,

1337
01:02:53,079 --> 01:02:55,480
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj naš misionar.

1338
01:02:55,480 --> 01:02:56,960
[SPEAKER_00] Malo je ono izletio,

1339
01:02:56,960 --> 01:02:58,579
[SPEAKER_00] tako s ovim primjerom,

1340
01:02:58,579 --> 01:03:00,400
[SPEAKER_00] ali kasnije se malo popravio

1341
01:03:00,400 --> 01:03:01,159
[SPEAKER_00] u smislu da je rekao

1342
01:03:01,159 --> 01:03:03,360
[SPEAKER_00] da ovaj nije ni čuo što je bilo.

1343
01:03:03,360 --> 01:03:06,039
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, on je rekao kao psovka Boga,

1344
01:03:06,039 --> 01:03:07,179
[SPEAKER_00] pa ovaj je rekao ja tebi,

1345
01:03:07,179 --> 01:03:08,619
[SPEAKER_00] pa ovaj je rekao,

1346
01:03:08,619 --> 01:03:09,800
[SPEAKER_00] njemu nije teški grijeh.

1347
01:03:09,800 --> 01:03:10,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ali onda se ispravio,

1348
01:03:10,840 --> 01:03:11,900
[SPEAKER_00] rekao, znači,

1349
01:03:11,900 --> 01:03:13,800
[SPEAKER_00] da ovaj nije ni čuo što je bilo i tako.

1350
01:03:13,840 --> 01:03:16,699
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, bi nije bio svjestan toga što je ovaj izgovorio.

1351
01:03:16,699 --> 01:03:18,260
[SPEAKER_00] U tom smislu.

1352
01:03:18,260 --> 01:03:19,639
[SPEAKER_00] E sada,

1353
01:03:19,639 --> 01:03:22,340
[SPEAKER_00] znači, razlika između svjestno i s namjerom.

1354
01:03:22,340 --> 01:03:25,760
[SPEAKER_00] Da bi bila namjera,

1355
01:03:25,760 --> 01:03:27,159
[SPEAKER_00] mora biti prvo svjestno.

1356
01:03:27,159 --> 01:03:28,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1357
01:03:28,679 --> 01:03:30,340
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, svjestan sam

1358
01:03:30,340 --> 01:03:31,840
[SPEAKER_00] da to što činim

1359
01:03:31,840 --> 01:03:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] je teški grijeh.

1360
01:03:34,039 --> 01:03:36,300
[SPEAKER_00] Sada, recimo, možemo uzeti za primjer ogovaranje.

1361
01:03:36,300 --> 01:03:37,860
[SPEAKER_00] To je onako dosta pristo, recimo,

1362
01:03:37,860 --> 01:03:39,239
[SPEAKER_00] među curama ovako zna bit.

1363
01:03:39,239 --> 01:03:41,780
[SPEAKER_00] To je, oj, ogovarala sam i prijateljice se našle,

1364
01:03:41,780 --> 01:03:43,239
[SPEAKER_00] znate, vele časni, to je tako,

1365
01:03:43,239 --> 01:03:43,900
[SPEAKER_00] evo, aaa.

1366
01:03:43,900 --> 01:03:45,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1367
01:03:45,980 --> 01:03:48,840
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, kad ogovaranje postaje teški grijeh?

1368
01:03:48,840 --> 01:03:50,840
[SPEAKER_00] Našle se vi,

1369
01:03:50,840 --> 01:03:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] sjele,

1370
01:03:52,539 --> 01:03:54,760
[SPEAKER_00] ti si prije,

1371
01:03:54,760 --> 01:03:56,239
[SPEAKER_00] o nismo se vidjeli sto godina,

1372
01:03:56,239 --> 01:03:57,500
[SPEAKER_00] šta ima, kako si mi,

1373
01:03:57,500 --> 01:03:58,219
[SPEAKER_00] sve super,

1374
01:03:58,219 --> 01:04:00,179
[SPEAKER_00] pa kako ti evo u životu,

1375
01:04:00,179 --> 01:04:01,960
[SPEAKER_00] pa dobro mi, evo, sve mi super ide,

1376
01:04:02,059 --> 01:04:03,460
[SPEAKER_00] pa polažem te ispred, trudim se,

1377
01:04:03,460 --> 01:04:04,579
[SPEAKER_00] ali

1378
01:04:04,579 --> 01:04:06,980
[SPEAKER_00] ona

1379
01:04:06,980 --> 01:04:10,059
[SPEAKER_00] me ubija, živciram i to,

1380
01:04:10,059 --> 01:04:11,380
[SPEAKER_00] ona

1381
01:04:11,380 --> 01:04:13,199
[SPEAKER_00] je

1382
01:04:13,199 --> 01:04:18,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ana me stvarno ubija.

1383
01:04:18,079 --> 01:04:20,900
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je postalo teški grijeh?

1384
01:04:20,900 --> 01:04:22,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ana.

1385
01:04:22,920 --> 01:04:28,219
[SPEAKER_00] Toko govorimo o nekakvoj situaciji,

1386
01:04:28,219 --> 01:04:30,340
[SPEAKER_00] gdje osoba koja je ispred mene

1387
01:04:30,340 --> 01:04:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] ne može ni znat o kom sad ni šta,

1388
01:04:32,059 --> 01:04:33,920
[SPEAKER_00] nego jednostavno me boli to i želim to iznijet,

1389
01:04:33,920 --> 01:04:36,199
[SPEAKER_00] to nije ogovaranje, to nije teški grijeh.

1390
01:04:36,199 --> 01:04:38,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kada govorimo o konkretnoj osobi,

1391
01:04:38,579 --> 01:04:39,900
[SPEAKER_00] onda postaje teški grijeh.

1392
01:04:39,900 --> 01:04:41,539
[SPEAKER_00] I još jedna stvar.

1393
01:04:41,539 --> 01:04:44,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ukoliko ćemo imati redovitu ispovjed,

1394
01:04:44,539 --> 01:04:46,320
[SPEAKER_00] i ukoliko ćemo redovito

1395
01:04:46,320 --> 01:04:48,440
[SPEAKER_00] pristupati sa kramentoje uharistije,

1396
01:04:48,440 --> 01:04:49,659
[SPEAKER_00] hraniti sa živim Kristom,

1397
01:04:49,659 --> 01:04:51,860
[SPEAKER_00] proradi će nam dobro i savjest.

1398
01:04:52,559 --> 01:04:54,940
[SPEAKER_00] i taj glas u nama, taj Božji glas u nama,

1399
01:04:54,940 --> 01:04:55,539
[SPEAKER_00] savjesti.

1400
01:04:55,539 --> 01:04:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] I kada krenemo, recimo, u nekakvo ogovaranje,

1401
01:04:59,099 --> 01:05:00,340
[SPEAKER_00] savjesti brzo kaže,

1402
01:05:00,340 --> 01:05:04,019
[SPEAKER_00] ej, stani, stani, stani, ne!

1403
01:05:06,019 --> 01:05:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je korak, ako prijeđem preko,

1404
01:05:09,500 --> 01:05:11,239
[SPEAKER_00] postaje teški grijeh.

1405
01:05:11,239 --> 01:05:12,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ako se zaustavim,

1406
01:05:12,679 --> 01:05:14,420
[SPEAKER_00] ne, ne želim,

1407
01:05:14,420 --> 01:05:15,980
[SPEAKER_00] onda nije teški grijeh,

1408
01:05:15,980 --> 01:05:17,460
[SPEAKER_00] jer nema namjere.

1409
01:05:17,460 --> 01:05:19,659
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, savjest mi je rekla,

1410
01:05:19,659 --> 01:05:21,179
[SPEAKER_00] svjestan sam da počinjem,

1411
01:05:21,179 --> 01:05:22,659
[SPEAKER_00] počinje biti,

1412
01:05:22,659 --> 01:05:23,679
[SPEAKER_00] postajem svjestan,

1413
01:05:23,679 --> 01:05:26,539
[SPEAKER_00] namjera postaje kada prijeđem taj korak

1414
01:05:26,539 --> 01:05:27,659
[SPEAKER_00] i kažem, ma boli me briga,

1415
01:05:27,659 --> 01:05:28,659
[SPEAKER_00] i nastavim dalje.

1416
01:05:28,659 --> 01:05:30,840
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, prvo je svjesnost,

1417
01:05:30,840 --> 01:05:33,159
[SPEAKER_00] a onda postaje namjera kada prijeđem taj korak.

1418
01:05:36,019 --> 01:05:38,239
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ukoliko, kažem, se dogodi ovo,

1419
01:05:38,239 --> 01:05:40,260
[SPEAKER_00] ne morate odmah trčati na izpovijed,

1420
01:05:40,260 --> 01:05:42,059
[SPEAKER_00] evo, ogovarala sam, moram se ispovjeti,

1421
01:05:42,059 --> 01:05:43,079
[SPEAKER_00] inače se ne mogu pričesti.

1422
01:05:43,079 --> 01:05:44,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ako si se zaustavila,

1423
01:05:44,699 --> 01:05:46,980
[SPEAKER_00] kada ti je gospodin rekao, nemoj.

1424
01:05:46,980 --> 01:05:49,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1425
01:05:49,960 --> 01:05:51,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ista stvar često puta, znaćem,

1426
01:05:51,960 --> 01:05:53,320
[SPEAKER_00] primjer, sad mi pada na pamet,

1427
01:05:53,320 --> 01:05:54,219
[SPEAKER_00] prisilne misli.

1428
01:05:54,219 --> 01:05:57,940
[SPEAKER_00] Jesu li prisilne misle teški grijeh,

1429
01:05:57,940 --> 01:05:59,079
[SPEAKER_00] zbog kojeg moraš na izpovijed?

1430
01:05:59,079 --> 01:06:02,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

1431
01:06:06,019 --> 01:06:08,559
[SPEAKER_00] prisilne misli.

1432
01:06:08,559 --> 01:06:10,880
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje je tu sloboda?

1433
01:06:10,880 --> 01:06:16,960
[SPEAKER_00] A ne, ona odmah trči,

1434
01:06:16,960 --> 01:06:18,179
[SPEAKER_00] veličasni, veličasni.

1435
01:06:18,179 --> 01:06:20,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ili on.

1436
01:06:20,619 --> 01:06:26,840
[SPEAKER_00] Jednom je jedan svečanik rekao,

1437
01:06:26,840 --> 01:06:29,659
[SPEAKER_00] jako teško, je teško sagriješiti.

1438
01:06:31,880 --> 01:06:34,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kada čovjek živi sakramentalno,

1439
01:06:34,019 --> 01:06:36,519
[SPEAKER_00] onda stvarno to postaje istina.

1440
01:06:36,519 --> 01:06:39,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ako živiš redovito,

1441
01:06:39,940 --> 01:06:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] molitveni plan imaš kroz svoj dan,

1442
01:06:43,539 --> 01:06:45,059
[SPEAKER_00] znači moliš redovito,

1443
01:06:45,059 --> 01:06:48,380
[SPEAKER_00] znači posebno ako imate odnos sa našom nebeskom majkom,

1444
01:06:48,380 --> 01:06:50,019
[SPEAKER_00] ako moli krunicu,

1445
01:06:50,019 --> 01:06:51,300
[SPEAKER_00] onako sa željom,

1446
01:06:51,300 --> 01:06:54,539
[SPEAKER_00] sa cvrštom željom da pripada našoj majici nebeskoj,

1447
01:06:54,539 --> 01:06:56,320
[SPEAKER_00] da se ne treba bojati grijeh,

1448
01:06:56,320 --> 01:06:58,239
[SPEAKER_00] ba, sigurno se ne treba bojati.

1449
01:06:58,239 --> 01:07:01,440
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nije bezvezen, jezno bezgrešno srce nam darovano.

1450
01:07:01,880 --> 01:07:03,860
[SPEAKER_00] Nego da nas čuva, da nam pomogne.

1451
01:07:03,860 --> 01:07:06,400
[SPEAKER_00] Znači redoviti molitveni život,

1452
01:07:06,400 --> 01:07:07,119
[SPEAKER_00] duhovni život,

1453
01:07:07,119 --> 01:07:08,880
[SPEAKER_00] redoviti sakramentalni život,

1454
01:07:08,880 --> 01:07:11,800
[SPEAKER_00] stvarno je jako teško, teško sagriješiti.

1455
01:07:11,800 --> 01:07:15,300
[SPEAKER_00] Može.

1456
01:07:15,300 --> 01:07:16,820
[SPEAKER_01] Rade.

1457
01:07:16,820 --> 01:07:19,699
[SPEAKER_01] I onda možda mala teže pitanje.

1458
01:07:19,699 --> 01:07:21,980
[SPEAKER_01] Unaprijed izrečena kazna,

1459
01:07:21,980 --> 01:07:22,800
[SPEAKER_01] ekskomunikacija,

1460
01:07:22,800 --> 01:07:25,280
[SPEAKER_01] i tako vjerujem da niko ovdje nema puno problema s tim,

1461
01:07:25,280 --> 01:07:27,340
[SPEAKER_01] ali vjerujem da ćemo se sretati,

1462
01:07:27,340 --> 01:07:30,099
[SPEAKER_01] srećemo sa ljudima možda koji po to spadaju,

1463
01:07:30,179 --> 01:07:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] pa evo možda par riječi o tome.

1464
01:07:32,000 --> 01:07:33,659
[SPEAKER_00] Aha, ekskomunikacija.

1465
01:07:33,659 --> 01:07:35,719
[SPEAKER_01] Ekskomunikacija, znači unaprijed izrečena kazna,

1466
01:07:35,719 --> 01:07:36,320
[SPEAKER_01] ekskomunikacija.

1467
01:07:36,320 --> 01:07:37,239
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, late sentencije.

1468
01:07:37,239 --> 01:07:38,079
[SPEAKER_00] Da, late sentencije.

1469
01:07:38,079 --> 01:07:41,699
[SPEAKER_00] To je naše interno.

1470
01:07:41,699 --> 01:07:43,380
[SPEAKER_00] Late sentencije.

1471
01:07:43,380 --> 01:07:53,539
[SPEAKER_00] Šta, mobitel?

1472
01:07:53,539 --> 01:07:55,619
[SPEAKER_00] Aha, nisam shvatio, ali ovo najveće.

1473
01:07:55,619 --> 01:08:00,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ekskomunikacija, znači, je odjeljno sa zajednice.

1474
01:08:00,860 --> 01:08:04,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kad gledaš u stvari, evo, to mi sad više primjera ovako kaže,

1475
01:08:04,300 --> 01:08:06,880
[SPEAKER_00] znači svaki grijeh u stvari pod navodnicima,

1476
01:08:06,880 --> 01:08:09,780
[SPEAKER_00] pod navodnicima postaje jedna ekskomunikacija u stvari.

1477
01:08:09,880 --> 01:08:12,519
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto? Zato što me grijeh oddjeljuje od gospodina,

1478
01:08:12,519 --> 01:08:14,780
[SPEAKER_00] teški grijeh, oddjeljuje me od zajednice.

1479
01:08:14,780 --> 01:08:17,680
[SPEAKER_00] Kao mistično tijelo Hristovo,

1480
01:08:17,680 --> 01:08:20,520
[SPEAKER_00] znači grijeh je protiv crkve, ja sam odvojeno i od crkve.

1481
01:08:20,520 --> 01:08:23,859
[SPEAKER_00] Griješim, to su one takozvane posljedice grijeha

1482
01:08:23,859 --> 01:08:27,039
[SPEAKER_00] koje ostaju od moga grijeha, znači od moga ranjavanja crkve.

1483
01:08:27,039 --> 01:08:29,880
[SPEAKER_00] Znači ja kada se oddjelim od Boga,

1484
01:08:29,880 --> 01:08:31,819
[SPEAKER_00] kada se oddjelim od glave, od Krista,

1485
01:08:31,819 --> 01:08:33,659
[SPEAKER_00] oddjelim se i od crkve, od zajednice.

1486
01:08:33,659 --> 01:08:36,520
[SPEAKER_00] Znači na taj način skoro svaki teški grijeh

1487
01:08:36,520 --> 01:08:38,680
[SPEAKER_00] postaje ekskomunikacija u tom smislu.

1488
01:08:38,680 --> 01:08:40,439
[SPEAKER_00] A ovo što Vigor spominje,

1489
01:08:40,439 --> 01:08:41,619
[SPEAKER_00] to je više znači onaj,

1490
01:08:41,619 --> 01:08:44,020
[SPEAKER_00] to su oni teški grijeh,

1491
01:08:44,020 --> 01:08:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] sad da ne ulazim previše u taj zakon

1492
01:08:46,000 --> 01:08:48,380
[SPEAKER_00] i kamarskog prava, recimo ako neko udari papu

1493
01:08:48,380 --> 01:08:50,300
[SPEAKER_00] ili svećenika

1494
01:08:50,300 --> 01:08:52,180
[SPEAKER_00] ili abortus,

1495
01:08:52,180 --> 01:08:53,239
[SPEAKER_00] isto tako da,

1496
01:08:53,239 --> 01:08:54,920
[SPEAKER_00] to su znači

1497
01:08:54,920 --> 01:08:58,520
[SPEAKER_00] grijeh koji su bili jedno vrijeme

1498
01:08:58,520 --> 01:09:01,260
[SPEAKER_00] čuvani na neki način,

1499
01:09:01,260 --> 01:09:03,500
[SPEAKER_00] znači mogao ih odriješiti samo,

1500
01:09:03,500 --> 01:09:06,439
[SPEAKER_00] znači ima ih pet, ako se ne varam,

1501
01:09:06,439 --> 01:09:08,819
[SPEAKER_00] onih koji može odriješiti samo sveta stolica,

1502
01:09:08,819 --> 01:09:12,460
[SPEAKER_00] znači, a grijeh abortusa bio jedno vrijeme vezan

1503
01:09:12,460 --> 01:09:13,159
[SPEAKER_00] uz biskupa

1504
01:09:13,159 --> 01:09:15,159
[SPEAKER_00] ili u jaka vremena crkve,

1505
01:09:15,159 --> 01:09:17,199
[SPEAKER_00] ali papa Franjo je onaj koji je

1506
01:09:17,199 --> 01:09:18,779
[SPEAKER_00] nakon veću godini milosrđa

1507
01:09:18,779 --> 01:09:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] i nakon godine milosrđa

1508
01:09:20,000 --> 01:09:21,500
[SPEAKER_00] dao svim svećenicima

1509
01:09:21,500 --> 01:09:23,260
[SPEAKER_00] znači tu vlast,

1510
01:09:23,260 --> 01:09:24,359
[SPEAKER_00] možemo reći da mogu

1511
01:09:24,359 --> 01:09:25,979
[SPEAKER_00] odriješiti od tih grijeha,

1512
01:09:26,020 --> 01:09:29,279
[SPEAKER_00] isto i vratiti opet u krilo crkve

1513
01:09:29,279 --> 01:09:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] na taj način.

1514
01:09:30,199 --> 01:09:31,619
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, ovaj,

1515
01:09:31,619 --> 01:09:34,479
[SPEAKER_00] znači, ekskomunikacija znači

1516
01:09:34,479 --> 01:09:36,560
[SPEAKER_00] da smo izašli iz crkvenog zajedništva,

1517
01:09:36,560 --> 01:09:38,760
[SPEAKER_00] a kada nismo u crkvenom zajedništvu,

1518
01:09:38,760 --> 01:09:40,539
[SPEAKER_00] onda nismo u zajedništvu ni s gospodinom,

1519
01:09:40,539 --> 01:09:41,520
[SPEAKER_00] ni s glavom

1520
01:09:41,520 --> 01:09:43,520
[SPEAKER_00] te crkve, tog tijela.

1521
01:09:43,520 --> 01:09:46,279
[SPEAKER_00] A ako nismo u zajedništvu s gospodinom,

1522
01:09:46,279 --> 01:09:48,180
[SPEAKER_00] ako umremo kao takvi,

1523
01:09:48,180 --> 01:09:50,739
[SPEAKER_00] znamo gdje ćemo završiti.

1524
01:09:50,739 --> 01:09:54,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ali,

1525
01:09:55,800 --> 01:09:56,819
[SPEAKER_00] da ne bude to sad ovako.

1526
01:09:56,819 --> 01:09:59,340
[SPEAKER_00] Koji grijeh

1527
01:09:59,340 --> 01:10:02,159
[SPEAKER_00] jedino

1528
01:10:02,159 --> 01:10:04,500
[SPEAKER_00] Bog ne može oprostiti?

1529
01:10:04,500 --> 01:10:05,920
[SPEAKER_00] Sad jedno pitanje je vam postavljeno.

1530
01:10:05,920 --> 01:10:08,359
[SPEAKER_00] A koji je to grijeh?

1531
01:10:08,359 --> 01:10:14,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ali još?

1532
01:10:14,659 --> 01:10:18,100
[SPEAKER_00] Koji bi bio grijeh

1533
01:10:18,100 --> 01:10:19,560
[SPEAKER_00] protiv Duha Svetoga?

1534
01:10:19,560 --> 01:10:20,680
[SPEAKER_00] Šta mislite?

1535
01:10:22,279 --> 01:10:25,279
[SPEAKER_00] njekanje nauka,

1536
01:10:25,279 --> 01:10:27,880
[SPEAKER_00] ustrojeno odbijanje

1537
01:10:27,880 --> 01:10:29,319
[SPEAKER_00] Božjeg postojanja, jel?

1538
01:10:29,319 --> 01:10:29,579
[SPEAKER_00] Šta?

1539
01:10:29,579 --> 01:10:31,899
[SPEAKER_00] Da Bog postoji.

1540
01:10:35,899 --> 01:10:37,920
[SPEAKER_00] Znate koji je jedini grijeh koji Bog ne može oprostiti?

1541
01:10:37,920 --> 01:10:40,880
[SPEAKER_00] I kada ga kažemo da nemamo grijeha,

1542
01:10:40,880 --> 01:10:43,619
[SPEAKER_00] jer onda nema šta oprostiti.

1543
01:10:47,300 --> 01:10:49,140
[SPEAKER_00] Grijeh protiv Duha Svetoga je reći

1544
01:10:49,140 --> 01:10:51,100
[SPEAKER_00] nemam grijeha.

1545
01:10:51,100 --> 01:10:52,899
[SPEAKER_00] Ne trebaš mi Bože.

1546
01:10:52,899 --> 01:10:54,399
[SPEAKER_00] Ustranjenost u ovome.

1547
01:10:54,399 --> 01:10:55,460
[SPEAKER_00] Sve što ste rekli, ali

1548
01:10:55,460 --> 01:10:57,319
[SPEAKER_00] Vigori je uvijek ovako dosta teološki,

1549
01:10:57,319 --> 01:10:57,939
[SPEAKER_00] onako, znaš,

1550
01:10:57,939 --> 01:10:58,699
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj nastrojen.

1551
01:10:58,699 --> 01:11:00,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ja to pokušavam ovako više,

1552
01:11:00,420 --> 01:11:01,539
[SPEAKER_00] više seljački,

1553
01:11:01,539 --> 01:11:01,859
[SPEAKER_00] onako,

1554
01:11:01,859 --> 01:11:02,399
[SPEAKER_00] laički.

1555
01:11:02,399 --> 01:11:05,380
[SPEAKER_00] Grijeh koji Bog ne može oprostiti,

1556
01:11:05,380 --> 01:11:05,739
[SPEAKER_00] jer reći,

1557
01:11:05,739 --> 01:11:06,760
[SPEAKER_00] ja nemam grijeha.

1558
01:11:08,039 --> 01:11:09,479
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nećete vjerovat.

1559
01:11:09,479 --> 01:11:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nećete vjerovat.

1560
01:11:11,000 --> 01:11:13,020
[SPEAKER_00] Koliki znaju ući u spredovnicu

1561
01:11:13,020 --> 01:11:13,239
[SPEAKER_00] i reći,

1562
01:11:13,239 --> 01:11:13,659
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj časni,

1563
01:11:13,659 --> 01:11:14,500
[SPEAKER_00] pa nemam baš grijeha.

1564
01:11:14,500 --> 01:11:18,359
[SPEAKER_00] Nažalost.

1565
01:11:18,359 --> 01:11:19,659
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono što sam rekao,

1566
01:11:19,659 --> 01:11:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] pio 11. ili 12.

1567
01:11:20,960 --> 01:11:21,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam sad koji je.

1568
01:11:21,920 --> 01:11:24,699
[SPEAKER_00] Najveći grijeh današnjice,

1569
01:11:24,699 --> 01:11:26,439
[SPEAKER_00] današnjeg čovjeka je to što je izgubio

1570
01:11:26,439 --> 01:11:27,220
[SPEAKER_00] osjećaj grijeha.

1571
01:11:27,220 --> 01:11:29,220
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nemam grijeha,

1572
01:11:29,220 --> 01:11:29,699
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj časni.

1573
01:11:29,699 --> 01:11:32,979
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ja volim reći onako,

1574
01:11:32,979 --> 01:11:33,840
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodžo,

1575
01:11:33,840 --> 01:11:36,760
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu hvala i slava.

1576
01:11:38,039 --> 01:11:39,180
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo odmah van.

1577
01:11:39,180 --> 01:11:41,420
[SPEAKER_00] Uzet ćemo Gospin kip,

1578
01:11:41,420 --> 01:11:42,720
[SPEAKER_00] maknut ćemo ga

1579
01:11:42,720 --> 01:11:44,180
[SPEAKER_00] i stavit ćemo vas.

1580
01:11:44,180 --> 01:11:47,960
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ona kaže,

1581
01:11:47,960 --> 01:11:50,340
[SPEAKER_00] pa nisam baš tako mislila.

1582
01:11:50,340 --> 01:11:56,420
[SPEAKER_00] Eto.

1583
01:11:56,420 --> 01:12:02,880
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo,

1584
01:12:02,880 --> 01:12:03,500
[SPEAKER_00] e, izvoli.

1585
01:12:07,460 --> 01:12:10,920
[SPEAKER_00] najbolje rješenje je razgovarati

1586
01:12:10,920 --> 01:12:11,739
[SPEAKER_00] sa svojim duhovnikom.

1587
01:12:11,739 --> 01:12:14,819
[SPEAKER_00] Treba imati duhovnika i razgovarati s nekim.

1588
01:12:14,819 --> 01:12:21,760
[SPEAKER_00] Pa moliti za ovu milost Božje ljubavi.

1589
01:12:21,760 --> 01:12:23,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš, kada me Božja ljubav dotakne,

1590
01:12:23,380 --> 01:12:24,500
[SPEAKER_00] kada osjetim da sam ljubljen,

1591
01:12:24,500 --> 01:12:25,520
[SPEAKER_00] onda ne mogu,

1592
01:12:25,520 --> 01:12:26,640
[SPEAKER_00] jednostavno, kažem,

1593
01:12:26,640 --> 01:12:28,300
[SPEAKER_00] sve to bude temelj svega,

1594
01:12:28,300 --> 01:12:29,159
[SPEAKER_00] krećemo od toga.

1595
01:12:29,159 --> 01:12:32,619
[SPEAKER_00] i onda neće gospodin dopustiti

1596
01:12:32,619 --> 01:12:33,739
[SPEAKER_00] da odiče ga napravim

1597
01:12:33,739 --> 01:12:34,699
[SPEAKER_00] od muhe, slona

1598
01:12:34,699 --> 01:12:35,600
[SPEAKER_00] i takve stvari,

1599
01:12:35,600 --> 01:12:36,500
[SPEAKER_00] znaš, u tom smislu.

1600
01:12:36,500 --> 01:12:38,220
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da,

1601
01:12:38,220 --> 01:12:39,340
[SPEAKER_00] to.

1602
01:12:39,340 --> 01:12:41,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ali i duhovnik.

1603
01:12:41,140 --> 01:12:42,939
[SPEAKER_00] Imati duhovnika,

1604
01:12:42,939 --> 01:12:44,039
[SPEAKER_00] razgovarati s duhovnikom.

1605
01:12:44,039 --> 01:12:45,619
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da,

1606
01:12:45,619 --> 01:12:46,619
[SPEAKER_00] i to isto je sigurno.

1607
01:12:46,619 --> 01:12:49,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ima još jedna stvar,

1608
01:12:49,239 --> 01:12:50,560
[SPEAKER_00] sad mi je pao na pamet,

1609
01:12:50,560 --> 01:12:52,760
[SPEAKER_00] kao koliko često se ispovijedat,

1610
01:12:52,760 --> 01:12:54,020
[SPEAKER_00] onda se zna,

1611
01:12:54,020 --> 01:12:54,800
[SPEAKER_00] ono, kaže se,

1612
01:12:54,800 --> 01:12:55,460
[SPEAKER_00] znači da, ne znam,

1613
01:12:55,460 --> 01:12:56,680
[SPEAKER_00] Leopold Bogdan Mandić,

1614
01:12:56,680 --> 01:12:58,319
[SPEAKER_00] otac Ante Antić,

1615
01:12:58,319 --> 01:13:02,279
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam još za koga sam čuo,

1616
01:13:02,279 --> 01:13:03,579
[SPEAKER_00] da su se ispovijedali svaki dan.

1617
01:13:03,579 --> 01:13:06,359
[SPEAKER_00] Čak mi je neko spomenuo

1618
01:13:06,359 --> 01:13:08,439
[SPEAKER_00] da je i Frabona Ventura Duda pokojni

1619
01:13:08,439 --> 01:13:09,840
[SPEAKER_00] da se ispovijedao isto.

1620
01:13:09,840 --> 01:13:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] Barim, ako ništa,

1621
01:13:10,960 --> 01:13:13,239
[SPEAKER_00] sigurno je u zadnjih tih mjeseci

1622
01:13:13,239 --> 01:13:14,260
[SPEAKER_00] dok je bio u bolnice

1623
01:13:14,260 --> 01:13:15,720
[SPEAKER_00] da se ispovijedao svaki dan.

1624
01:13:16,619 --> 01:13:19,300
[SPEAKER_00] Znači li to sada,

1625
01:13:19,300 --> 01:13:20,739
[SPEAKER_00] jednom je neko mi je došao

1626
01:13:20,739 --> 01:13:22,340
[SPEAKER_00] i sad par dana za redom

1627
01:13:22,340 --> 01:13:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi mi svaki dan osoba

1628
01:13:23,539 --> 01:13:24,260
[SPEAKER_00] u ispovijedalnicu

1629
01:13:24,260 --> 01:13:25,119
[SPEAKER_00] i sad nakon nekog redna

1630
01:13:25,119 --> 01:13:25,939
[SPEAKER_00] ja kažem pa dobro,

1631
01:13:25,939 --> 01:13:27,680
[SPEAKER_00] pa svešto baš svaki dan.

1632
01:13:27,680 --> 01:13:28,760
[SPEAKER_00] Pa otac Ante Antić

1633
01:13:28,760 --> 01:13:29,720
[SPEAKER_00] si ispovijedao svaki dan.

1634
01:13:29,720 --> 01:13:32,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ante, pa nisam te prepoznao.

1635
01:13:32,619 --> 01:13:38,920
[SPEAKER_00] Nisi otac Ante Antić.

1636
01:13:38,920 --> 01:13:44,220
[SPEAKER_00] Ako se Leopold Bogdan Mandić

1637
01:13:44,220 --> 01:13:45,039
[SPEAKER_00] ispovijedao svaki dan,

1638
01:13:45,039 --> 01:13:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] to je Leopold Bogdan Mandić.

1639
01:13:46,619 --> 01:13:49,300
[SPEAKER_00] to ne znači da moramo mi.

1640
01:13:51,300 --> 01:13:52,899
[SPEAKER_00] gospodin će pokazati koliko.

1641
01:13:55,979 --> 01:13:56,939
[SPEAKER_00] i važno je boriti se,

1642
01:13:56,939 --> 01:13:57,560
[SPEAKER_00] ne odustajati,

1643
01:13:57,560 --> 01:13:58,020
[SPEAKER_00] boriti se.

1644
01:13:58,020 --> 01:13:59,380
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ste u problemima,

1645
01:13:59,380 --> 01:14:00,159
[SPEAKER_00] sjetite se mene.

1646
01:14:00,659 --> 01:14:01,159
[SPEAKER_00] boriti se.

1647
01:14:01,159 --> 01:14:01,659
[SPEAKER_00] Boriti se.

1648
01:14:01,659 --> 01:14:02,979
[SPEAKER_00] I boriti se.

1649
01:14:02,979 --> 01:14:04,760
[SPEAKER_00] Boriti se.

1650
01:14:04,760 --> 01:14:05,800
[SPEAKER_00] Boriti se.

1651
01:14:05,800 --> 01:14:08,180
[SPEAKER_00] Zazivajte moje ime.

1652
01:14:14,180 --> 01:14:15,640
[SPEAKER_00] treba se.

1653
01:14:15,640 --> 01:14:17,199
[SPEAKER_00] Neki dan sam govorio,

1654
01:14:17,199 --> 01:14:18,420
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo u duhovnom ratu.

1655
01:14:19,420 --> 01:14:20,020
[SPEAKER_00] časa mi rekao.

1656
01:14:20,020 --> 01:14:20,619
[SPEAKER_00] Časa mi rekao sretno.

1657
01:14:20,619 --> 01:14:22,399
[SPEAKER_00] Kad me jednom poslala tamo

1658
01:14:22,399 --> 01:14:23,239
[SPEAKER_00] iz Sakristije.

1659
01:14:23,239 --> 01:14:24,159
[SPEAKER_00] Je, sretno.

1660
01:14:24,159 --> 01:14:24,760
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo u rat.

1661
01:14:24,760 --> 01:14:25,779
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo u ratu.

1662
01:14:25,779 --> 01:14:26,880
[SPEAKER_00] I treba se boriti.

1663
01:14:26,880 --> 01:14:28,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ne odustajati,

1664
01:14:28,380 --> 01:14:29,140
[SPEAKER_00] ne se bojati.

1665
01:14:29,140 --> 01:14:30,359
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

1666
01:14:30,359 --> 01:14:31,720
[SPEAKER_00] Jer imamo pobjednika.

1667
01:14:31,720 --> 01:14:34,460
[SPEAKER_00] On je pobjedio,

1668
01:14:34,460 --> 01:14:35,439
[SPEAKER_00] uskrsnuo je,

1669
01:14:35,439 --> 01:14:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] živ je.

1670
01:14:38,100 --> 01:14:39,600
[SPEAKER_00] I zato se borimo.

1671
01:14:39,600 --> 01:14:41,920
[SPEAKER_00] Jer pobjednik je s nama.

1672
01:14:41,920 --> 01:14:45,340
[SPEAKER_00] I sve dok se ne vrati,

1673
01:14:45,340 --> 01:14:46,840
[SPEAKER_00] ustrajemo u borbi.

1674
01:14:46,840 --> 01:14:48,500
[SPEAKER_00] I ne odustajemo.

1675
01:14:48,500 --> 01:14:51,260
[SPEAKER_00] Jer znamo da je pobjeda naša.

1676
01:14:51,260 --> 01:14:56,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ima li još koje pitanje?

1677
01:14:56,680 --> 01:14:58,680
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam im skuži da gore ima ljudi.

1678
01:14:58,680 --> 01:15:00,479
[SPEAKER_00] Ona gore maše.

1679
01:15:00,479 --> 01:15:04,939
[SPEAKER_00] Imam ja jedno pitanje.

1680
01:15:04,939 --> 01:15:05,699
[SPEAKER_02] Može.

1681
01:15:06,319 --> 01:15:08,539
[SPEAKER_02] Granica između prosuđivanja i osuđivanja.

1682
01:15:08,539 --> 01:15:09,699
[SPEAKER_02] Gdje bi ju postavili?

1683
01:15:09,699 --> 01:15:11,100
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam oprosti, nisam dobro čuo.

1684
01:15:11,100 --> 01:15:12,500
[SPEAKER_00] Razlika između?

1685
01:15:12,500 --> 01:15:13,880
[SPEAKER_02] Granica, granica.

1686
01:15:13,880 --> 01:15:16,239
[SPEAKER_02] Kod prosuđivanja i osuđivanja.

1687
01:15:16,239 --> 01:15:18,180
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, svijestiti smo da postoje problemi

1688
01:15:18,180 --> 01:15:20,319
[SPEAKER_02] u kojih moramo biti svjesni,

1689
01:15:20,319 --> 01:15:22,380
[SPEAKER_02] ali gdje je granica gdje bi mogli,

1690
01:15:22,380 --> 01:15:24,439
[SPEAKER_02] ja imamo, reći podvuči crtu

1691
01:15:24,439 --> 01:15:26,720
[SPEAKER_02] i reći, ok, ovo je prosudba, ovo je osuđivanja.

1692
01:15:26,720 --> 01:15:27,460
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek ti je dobro,

1693
01:15:27,460 --> 01:15:29,359
[SPEAKER_00] i pitanje i ogovaranje, osuđivanja,

1694
01:15:29,420 --> 01:15:30,819
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek je dobro sebi posvijestiti,

1695
01:15:30,819 --> 01:15:32,479
[SPEAKER_00] mogu li ja to reći pred tojom osobom.

1696
01:15:32,479 --> 01:15:36,279
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, mogu li reći u njeznoj prisutnosti.

1697
01:15:36,279 --> 01:15:39,979
[SPEAKER_00] Ako u njeznoj prisutnosti ja mogu to reći,

1698
01:15:39,979 --> 01:15:41,060
[SPEAKER_00] onda je to prosuđivanje.

1699
01:15:43,380 --> 01:15:45,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ako se ne usudim reći to u njeznoj prisutnosti,

1700
01:15:45,279 --> 01:15:46,119
[SPEAKER_00] onda osuđujem.

1701
01:15:46,119 --> 01:15:49,319
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek je to dobar kriterij.

1702
01:15:49,319 --> 01:15:56,199
[SPEAKER_00] Dobar kriterij je uvijek staviti drugoga ispred sebe.

1703
01:15:56,199 --> 01:16:01,020
[SPEAKER_00] I još ono, jedno famozno, onaj prekrasno,

1704
01:16:01,020 --> 01:16:03,520
[SPEAKER_00] ja ga toliko volim, Papa Franjoga isto jako voli.

1705
01:16:03,520 --> 01:16:07,439
[SPEAKER_00] Što bi Isus učinio na tvojome mjestu?

1706
01:16:07,439 --> 01:16:10,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to je to.

1707
01:16:13,380 --> 01:16:33,880
[SPEAKER_00] To je, prvim znači, teško pitanje,

1708
01:16:33,880 --> 01:16:39,239
[SPEAKER_00] jer je stvari osobne, naravno je u smislu pred gospodinom.

1709
01:16:39,239 --> 01:16:42,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ta osoba, taj voditelj mora pred gospodinom, znaš,

1710
01:16:42,420 --> 01:16:43,840
[SPEAKER_00] biti u miru, njegova savijest,

1711
01:16:43,840 --> 01:16:46,579
[SPEAKER_00] i onda boriti se ovo, hrabro ustrajeti u svojoj odluci.

1712
01:16:46,579 --> 01:16:49,060
[SPEAKER_00] Odluku koju donese, treba hrabro držati.

1713
01:16:49,060 --> 01:16:49,939
[SPEAKER_00] Onda taj smjer.

1714
01:16:49,939 --> 01:16:52,560
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je to izmolio, ako je to donio pred gospodina, znaš.

1715
01:16:52,560 --> 01:16:54,199
[SPEAKER_00] To je poprilično osobno,

1716
01:16:54,199 --> 01:16:56,739
[SPEAKER_00] teško je dati neki generalni odgovor, opći da.

1717
01:16:56,739 --> 01:16:59,720
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, što bi Isus učinio?

1718
01:16:59,720 --> 01:17:03,640
[SPEAKER_00] Što bi Isus učinio?

1719
01:17:03,640 --> 01:17:07,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ali odlično, to ovako može kao floskula biti.

1720
01:17:07,880 --> 01:17:11,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ako počnete stvarno živjet tako život i postavite si pitanje o tim situacijama,

1721
01:17:11,800 --> 01:17:12,939
[SPEAKER_00] što bi Isus učinio?

1722
01:17:12,939 --> 01:17:15,100
[SPEAKER_00] Imao sam jednom,

1723
01:17:15,100 --> 01:17:17,720
[SPEAKER_00] negdje me

1724
01:17:17,720 --> 01:17:19,760
[SPEAKER_00] prije,

1725
01:17:19,760 --> 01:17:22,260
[SPEAKER_00] bilo je, bilo je ovo ljeto i onda,

1726
01:17:22,260 --> 01:17:25,579
[SPEAKER_00] ljetno vrijeme, onda je bilo kao to oblačenje od crkvi i tako neke stvari.

1727
01:17:25,579 --> 01:17:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] To onda kao,

1728
01:17:26,420 --> 01:17:28,220
[SPEAKER_00] posebno tu cure, čak i dečki,

1729
01:17:28,220 --> 01:17:29,699
[SPEAKER_00] već sam ja tu izviko se na ove,

1730
01:17:29,699 --> 01:17:31,220
[SPEAKER_00] u kratkim hlačama i tako,

1731
01:17:31,220 --> 01:17:32,479
[SPEAKER_00] rekao sam to, ništa od toga.

1732
01:17:33,159 --> 01:17:37,460
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, kako se smijem obući, što mogu obući, što se mogu staviti.

1733
01:17:37,460 --> 01:17:41,439
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro je pitanje, mogu li takva ili takav doći pred gospodina?

1734
01:17:41,439 --> 01:17:47,399
[SPEAKER_00] Danas sam baš na mobitelu dobiju jednu sliku, su mi poslali onako,

1735
01:17:47,399 --> 01:17:51,939
[SPEAKER_00] na engleskom je, sad neću,

1736
01:17:51,939 --> 01:17:54,239
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da je neću uspeti naći.

1737
01:17:54,239 --> 01:17:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kao ono, muškarci, slika muškaraca, znaš,

1738
01:17:57,079 --> 01:17:58,340
[SPEAKER_00] svi u crkvi, samo muškarci,

1739
01:17:58,340 --> 01:18:00,359
[SPEAKER_00] i svi u odijelima i u kravatama i kleče.

1740
01:18:00,359 --> 01:18:02,859
[SPEAKER_00] I onda nešto u stilu je kao,

1741
01:18:02,859 --> 01:18:05,819
[SPEAKER_00] ovi znaju da su došli

1742
01:18:05,819 --> 01:18:08,359
[SPEAKER_00] pred onoga

1743
01:18:08,359 --> 01:18:10,819
[SPEAKER_00] koji im je darovao život

1744
01:18:10,819 --> 01:18:12,659
[SPEAKER_00] i onoga koji ih je stvorio,

1745
01:18:12,659 --> 01:18:14,600
[SPEAKER_00] i onoga koji ih, znaš, tako u tom stilu.

1746
01:18:14,600 --> 01:18:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] Pred koga dolazim?

1747
01:18:16,500 --> 01:18:20,100
[SPEAKER_00] Posvijestiti sebi pred koga dolazim?

1748
01:18:20,100 --> 01:18:21,260
[SPEAKER_00] Pred kralja kraljeva,

1749
01:18:21,260 --> 01:18:23,039
[SPEAKER_00] pred sve mogućeg Boga.

1750
01:18:23,039 --> 01:18:25,340
[SPEAKER_00] Kakav dolazim?

1751
01:18:27,000 --> 01:18:28,640
[SPEAKER_00] Sad onda tu pitanje te čednosti,

1752
01:18:28,640 --> 01:18:29,460
[SPEAKER_00] recimo, kod cura,

1753
01:18:29,460 --> 01:18:30,340
[SPEAKER_00] kako se smije mogući,

1754
01:18:30,340 --> 01:18:31,880
[SPEAKER_00] ako oću li ga izazivati.

1755
01:18:31,880 --> 01:18:34,439
[SPEAKER_00] Neka opća pravila postoje u crkvi,

1756
01:18:34,439 --> 01:18:35,939
[SPEAKER_00] recimo, da su pokrivene ramena,

1757
01:18:35,939 --> 01:18:38,739
[SPEAKER_00] haljine ispod koljena i tako dalje.

1758
01:18:38,739 --> 01:18:40,819
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš, do koljena, ispod koljena u tom smislu.

1759
01:18:40,819 --> 01:18:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] Kod muških, znači, i duge hlače,

1760
01:18:43,539 --> 01:18:45,220
[SPEAKER_00] ne karatke hlače, ne japanke

1761
01:18:45,220 --> 01:18:46,859
[SPEAKER_00] i takve stvari, znači, ne, ono,

1762
01:18:46,859 --> 01:18:47,420
[SPEAKER_00] ići na plažu.

1763
01:18:47,420 --> 01:18:49,840
[SPEAKER_00] To su neka konkretna pravila oblačenja.

1764
01:18:49,840 --> 01:18:51,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ali pitanje čednosti je,

1765
01:18:52,979 --> 01:18:54,979
[SPEAKER_00] mogu vas evo, cure, malo utješiti.

1766
01:18:54,979 --> 01:18:55,859
[SPEAKER_00] Često puta,

1767
01:18:55,859 --> 01:18:57,779
[SPEAKER_00] u stvari,

1768
01:18:57,779 --> 01:19:00,420
[SPEAKER_00] ona koja sebe već pita to pitanje,

1769
01:19:00,420 --> 01:19:02,380
[SPEAKER_00] već je na jako dobrom putu,

1770
01:19:02,380 --> 01:19:03,380
[SPEAKER_00] jer je svjesna toga

1771
01:19:03,380 --> 01:19:04,560
[SPEAKER_00] i želi na tome raditi,

1772
01:19:04,560 --> 01:19:05,060
[SPEAKER_00] to je super.

1773
01:19:05,859 --> 01:19:07,380
[SPEAKER_00] A druga stvar je, nije vaš problem,

1774
01:19:07,380 --> 01:19:08,319
[SPEAKER_00] nego problem je dečki,

1775
01:19:08,319 --> 01:19:09,760
[SPEAKER_00] nažalost.

1776
01:19:09,760 --> 01:19:12,880
[SPEAKER_00] Problem je, su prljave oči.

1777
01:19:12,880 --> 01:19:15,899
[SPEAKER_00] I tu dečki treba moliti za čiste oči,

1778
01:19:15,899 --> 01:19:16,760
[SPEAKER_00] za čisti pogled.

1779
01:19:16,760 --> 01:19:20,699
[SPEAKER_00] Jer, i da dođeš u vreći krompira,

1780
01:19:20,699 --> 01:19:22,140
[SPEAKER_00] ako su njemu prljave oči,

1781
01:19:22,140 --> 01:19:22,819
[SPEAKER_00] džabati.

1782
01:19:26,039 --> 01:19:27,380
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da ovaj,

1783
01:19:27,380 --> 01:19:28,640
[SPEAKER_00] naravno,

1784
01:19:28,640 --> 01:19:31,140
[SPEAKER_00] trudit se znači

1785
01:19:31,140 --> 01:19:32,779
[SPEAKER_00] oblači čedno,

1786
01:19:32,779 --> 01:19:35,340
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne od toga raditi sad

1787
01:19:35,340 --> 01:19:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] preveliku sad,

1788
01:19:37,960 --> 01:19:39,220
[SPEAKER_00] evo, frku u tom smislu.

1789
01:19:39,220 --> 01:19:40,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ako takva,

1790
01:19:40,159 --> 01:19:41,439
[SPEAKER_00] možeš doći pred gospodina,

1791
01:19:41,439 --> 01:19:42,239
[SPEAKER_00] pred Isusa,

1792
01:19:42,239 --> 01:19:43,359
[SPEAKER_00] ne brini se.

1793
01:19:43,359 --> 01:19:45,220
[SPEAKER_00] Onda je njegov problem to.

1794
01:19:45,220 --> 01:19:47,159
[SPEAKER_00] On treba na tome raditi.

1795
01:19:47,159 --> 01:19:51,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ali da trebamo čuvati jedne druge,

1796
01:19:51,779 --> 01:19:52,220
[SPEAKER_00] trebamo.

1797
01:19:52,220 --> 01:19:53,720
[SPEAKER_00] Trebamo se paziti,

1798
01:19:53,720 --> 01:19:55,100
[SPEAKER_00] trebamo se čuvati međusobno.

1799
01:19:55,300 --> 01:19:55,979
[SPEAKER_00] čuvati oči,

1800
01:19:55,979 --> 01:19:58,100
[SPEAKER_00] čuvati pogled.

1801
01:19:58,100 --> 01:20:00,359
[SPEAKER_00] Volim jednu molitvu,

1802
01:20:00,359 --> 01:20:02,939
[SPEAKER_00] a to se dugo već moli,

1803
01:20:02,939 --> 01:20:03,840
[SPEAKER_00] u stvari u crkvi,

1804
01:20:03,840 --> 01:20:04,939
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da od

1805
01:20:04,939 --> 01:20:06,859
[SPEAKER_00] toga stoljećima već,

1806
01:20:06,859 --> 01:20:08,319
[SPEAKER_00] su te tri zdravo Marije,

1807
01:20:08,319 --> 01:20:10,239
[SPEAKER_00] molitva tri zdravo Marije.

1808
01:20:10,239 --> 01:20:12,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ne često volim moliti na večer,

1809
01:20:12,180 --> 01:20:13,899
[SPEAKER_00] stvari prije spavanje,

1810
01:20:13,899 --> 01:20:15,180
[SPEAKER_00] jedna od mojih molitava je

1811
01:20:15,180 --> 01:20:16,760
[SPEAKER_00] tri zdravo Marije za čisto srce,

1812
01:20:16,760 --> 01:20:18,380
[SPEAKER_00] a dušu i pogled,

1813
01:20:18,380 --> 01:20:19,039
[SPEAKER_00] i tijelo.

1814
01:20:19,039 --> 01:20:21,939
[SPEAKER_00] I funkcionira.

1815
01:20:21,939 --> 01:20:24,420
[SPEAKER_00] Nije baš lako,

1816
01:20:24,560 --> 01:20:25,520
[SPEAKER_00] borbe su tu,

1817
01:20:25,520 --> 01:20:26,159
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek.

1818
01:20:26,159 --> 01:20:27,260
[SPEAKER_00] Slabi smo,

1819
01:20:27,260 --> 01:20:28,399
[SPEAKER_00] to je ona konkupišencija,

1820
01:20:28,399 --> 01:20:29,560
[SPEAKER_00] ona navjezanost na grijeh.

1821
01:20:29,560 --> 01:20:31,159
[SPEAKER_00] Slabo smo tu,

1822
01:20:31,159 --> 01:20:33,560
[SPEAKER_00] ali ako se gospi preporučite

1823
01:20:33,560 --> 01:20:35,020
[SPEAKER_00] posebno kvitanju čistoće,

1824
01:20:35,020 --> 01:20:36,640
[SPEAKER_00] to vam je moje osobno iskustvo,

1825
01:20:36,640 --> 01:20:37,060
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne moje,

1826
01:20:37,060 --> 01:20:38,100
[SPEAKER_00] nego svih svijetaca.

1827
01:20:38,100 --> 01:20:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] Onaj koji s gospom živi,

1828
01:20:41,380 --> 01:20:43,100
[SPEAKER_00] borbu sa čistoćom,

1829
01:20:43,100 --> 01:20:44,220
[SPEAKER_00] zajedno s njom,

1830
01:20:44,220 --> 01:20:46,239
[SPEAKER_00] puno lakše vodite.

1831
01:20:47,100 --> 01:20:47,939
[SPEAKER_00] borbu za čistoću,

1832
01:20:47,939 --> 01:20:48,699
[SPEAKER_00] ne s čistoćom.

1833
01:20:48,699 --> 01:20:50,420
[SPEAKER_00] I smočevali,

1834
01:20:50,420 --> 01:20:51,300
[SPEAKER_00] borim se s čistoćom,

1835
01:20:51,300 --> 01:20:52,159
[SPEAKER_00] neću,

1836
01:20:52,159 --> 01:20:52,880
[SPEAKER_00] neću,

1837
01:20:52,880 --> 01:20:53,600
[SPEAKER_00] makni se.

1838
01:20:53,600 --> 01:20:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ne trebaš mi.

